00:02:44.140 --> 00:02:46.570
你们吵完以后呢？
What happened after you argued with your wife?

00:02:47.740 --> 00:02:49.510
她收拾行李
She packed a bag.

00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:53.840
去跟昆汀住……
She packed a bag to go and stay with Mr. Quentin.

00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:58.580
格伦·昆汀  乡村俱乐部的高尔夫球教练
Glenn Quentin, golf pro at the Snowden Hills Country Club...

00:02:58.790 --> 00:03:01.920
你最近才发现  他是你太太的情夫
whom you had discovered was your wife's lover.

00:03:04.230 --> 00:03:05.590
你跟踪她吗？
Did you follow her?

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:08.360
我先去酒吧买醉
I went to a few bars first.

00:03:09.070 --> 00:03:13.430
然后去他家  但没人在
Later, I drove to his house to confront them. They weren't home.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.060
我停了车
I parked in the turnout...

00:03:16.300 --> 00:03:17.290
等他们
and waited.

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:19.100
用意何在？
With what intention?

00:03:19.710 --> 00:03:21.140
我不确定
I'm not sure.

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:23.770
我醉了
I was confused...

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:25.060
糊里糊涂
drunk.

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:28.120
我想……
I think...

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:30.170
最多只是吓吓他们
mostly I wanted to scare them.

00:03:30.350 --> 00:03:33.750
结果他们一回来  你就冲进屋杀了他们
When they arrived, you went up to the house and murdered them.

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:36.110
不  我逐渐酒醒
I was sobering up.

00:03:36.260 --> 00:03:39.420
开车回家睡觉
I got back in the car and I drove home to sleep it off.

00:03:40.130 --> 00:03:43.100
路中把枪丢入皇家河
Along the way, I threw my gun into the Royal River.

00:03:43.300 --> 00:03:45.290
我已讲得很清楚
I've been very clear on this point.

00:03:45.540 --> 00:03:49.600
但清洁妇隔天早晨上工时
I get hazy where the cleaning woman shows up the following morning...

00:03:49.810 --> 00:03:52.400
发现床上的二人尸体
and finds your wife in bed with her lover...

00:03:52.610 --> 00:03:54.700
身上满是点三八的弹孔
riddled with.38-caliber bullets.

00:03:56.080 --> 00:04:00.280
你不觉得这很巧吗？  还是只有我这么想？
Does that strike you as a fantastic coincidence, or is it just me?

00:04:01.180 --> 00:04:02.170
是很巧
Yes, it does.

00:04:02.390 --> 00:04:05.550
但你仍声称早在案发之前
Yet you still maintain you threw your gun into the river...

00:04:05.810 --> 00:04:07.870
就已丢弃了枪
before the murders took place.

00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:10.250
这种说法倒是很省事
That's very convenient.

00:04:10.460 --> 00:04:12.120
这是实话
It's the truth.

00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:17.060
警方打捞三天都没找到
The police dragged that river for three days, and nary a gun was found...

00:04:17.230 --> 00:04:21.640
这样就无法比对你的手枪和
so no comparison could be made between your gun and the bullets...

00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:25.060
从受害人血尸内取出的弹头
taken from the bloodstained corpses of the victims.

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:28.080
所以呢
And that also...

00:04:28.540 --> 00:04:31.980
这样也非常省事  不是吗  杜弗伦先生
is very convenient. Isn't it, Mr. Dufresne?

00:04:33.320 --> 00:04:35.380
我是清白的
Since I am innocent of this crime...

00:04:35.590 --> 00:04:40.220
所以找不到枪  反倒对我非常不利
I find it decidedly inconvenient that the gun was never found.

00:04:58.110 --> 00:05:01.470
一切证据都向各位指明了案情
Ladies and gentlemen, you've heard all the evidence.

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:05.510
脚印和胎痕证明被告在场
We have the accused at the scene of the crime. We have footprints.

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:08.580
散落地面的子弹上有他的指纹
Bullets on the ground bearing his fingerprints.

00:05:08.790 --> 00:05:11.750
酒瓶碎片上同样也有指痕
A broken bourbon bottle, likewise with fingerprints.

00:05:11.950 --> 00:05:13.510
最重要的是
And most of all...

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:16.780
一位美女与情夫
we have a beautiful young woman and her lover...

00:05:16.990 --> 00:05:19.020
相拥而死
lying dead in each other's arms.

00:05:20.200 --> 00:05:22.820
他们是有伤风化
They had sinned.

00:05:24.030 --> 00:05:26.560
但是
But was their crime so great...

00:05:26.840 --> 00:05:29.030
罪该致死吗？
as to merit a death sentence?

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:31.540
与此同时  请各位
While you think about that...

00:05:32.980 --> 00:05:34.770
再考虑一件事
think about this:

00:05:35.650 --> 00:05:38.030
一只左轮手枪只能装六发子弹  而非八发
