早上十点坐成排
wound up sitting in a row at 10:00 in the morning...

00:37:37.800 --> 00:37:43.260
喝着冰镇啤酒
drinking icy-cold beer, courtesy of the hardest screw...

00:37:43.470 --> 00:37:46.740
肖申克监狱历来最狠的狱官请的客
that ever walked a turn at Shawshank State Prison.

00:37:46.940 --> 00:37:49.380
娘儿们  趁凉快喝
Drink up while it's cold, ladies.

00:37:50.480 --> 00:37:55.040
这王八蛋还装大方呢
The colossal prick even managed to sound magnanimous.

00:37:56.180 --> 00:38:00.640
阳光洒肩头  仿佛自由人
We sat and drank with the sun on our shoulders and felt like free men.

00:38:01.020 --> 00:38:04.460
像在修缮自家屋顶
We could have been tarring the roof of one of our own houses.

00:38:04.660 --> 00:38:07.490
像是造物主般自在
We were the lords of all creation.

00:38:08.060 --> 00:38:09.650
安迪呢……
As for Andy...

00:38:09.900 --> 00:38:12.530
他窝在凉荫下
he spent that break hunkered in the shade...

00:38:12.730 --> 00:38:15.220
脸上挂着奇异微笑
a strange little smile on his face...

00:38:15.470 --> 00:38:17.660
