I think it'll take years.

00:39:23.600 --> 00:39:26.130
时间有的是  就是缺石头
Years I got. What I don't have are the rocks.

00:39:26.340 --> 00:39:28.310
操场很贫瘠
Pickings are pretty slim in the yard.

00:39:28.510 --> 00:39:30.340
多半是石子
Pebbles, mostly.

00:39:34.680 --> 00:39:37.480
咱们算是朋友吧？
We're getting to be kind of friends, aren't we?

00:39:38.350 --> 00:39:39.910
算是吧
Yeah, I guess.

00:39:40.550 --> 00:39:42.080
能问你个问题吗
Can I ask you something?

00:39:43.560 --> 00:39:44.990
