-我知道什么？  -原来你不知道
-How did I know what?  -So you don't know.

00:41:12.310 --> 00:41:13.470
来
Come.

00:41:15.980 --> 00:41:18.080
歌女在这里
This is where the canary is.

00:41:20.750 --> 00:41:24.090
没想到她来寒舍献唱吧
Quite a surprise to hear a woman singing in my house, eh?

00:41:27.600 --> 00:41:28.990
的确……
That's quite a...

00:41:29.930 --> 00:41:31.590
