surprise.

00:41:34.000 --> 00:41:35.130
瑞德
Red

00:41:35.900 --> 00:41:37.300
等一下
Wait, wait.

00:41:37.840 --> 00:41:39.330
她要上场了
Here she comes.

00:41:39.610 --> 00:41:42.470
我最迷她甩头发的骚样
I like this part when she does that shit with her hair.

00:41:42.680 --> 00:41:45.410
这个月看过三场了
I know. I've seen it three times this month.

00:41:45.610 --> 00:41:47.510
姬旦  你衣着整齐吗？
Gilda, are you decent?

00:41:48.520 --> 00:41:49.640
在说我？
Me?

00:41:52.350 --> 00:41:54.120
我爱死这段了
God, I love it.

00:41:59.290 --> 00:42:02.290
听说阁下有求必应
I understand you're a man that knows how to get things.

00:42:03.300 --> 00:42:07.030
在下确非浪得虚名  你要什么？
I'm known to locate certain things from time to time. What do you want?

00:42:07.230 --> 00:42:09.360
-丽塔·海华丝  -什么？
-Rita Hayworth. -What?

00:42:09.940 --> 00:42:11.300
弄得到吗？
Can you get her?

00:42:12.710 --> 00:42:16.070
这位就是约翰尼·法雷尔啊  久仰久仰
So this is Johnny Farrel. I've heard a lot about you.

00:42:17.310 --> 00:42:19.610
-要几个星期  -几星期？
-Take a few weeks. -Weeks?

00:42:19.810 --> 00:42:24.220
我又没把她压在下面  抱歉这么说
I don't have her stuffed down the front of my pants right now, sorry to say.

00:42:24.400 --> 00:42:25.030
沉住气哦  法雷尔先生

00:42:25.130 --> 00:42:26.310
反正弄得到
But I'll get her.

00:42:26.320 --> 00:42:27.650
放心
Relax.

00:42:29.520 --> 00:42:30.820
谢了
Thanks.

00:42:31.660 --> 00:42:34.150
的确  你该见见他

00:42:34.400 --> 00:42:36.090
说了我来做什么吗？

00:42:36.430 --> 00:42:38.920
不  我要让他惊喜

00:42:51.210 --> 00:42:53.180
-出去  -我得放映
-Get out!  -I got to change reels!

00:42:53.410 --> 00:42:55.410
我叫你滚
I said fuck off!

00:43:01.560 --> 00:43:02.920
你不尖叫吗？
Ain't you going to scream?

00:43:04.260 --> 00:43:06.120
咱们算算总帐
Let's get this over with.

00:43:11.230 --> 00:43:13.220
他打破我鼻子
He broke my fucking nose!

00:43:22.540 --> 00:43:23.770
现在
Now...

00:43:24.240 --> 00:43:26.410
我要解拉链
I'm going to open my fly...

00:43:26.680 --> 00:43:29.440
叫你含什么你就含
and you'll swallow what I give you to swallow.

00:43:30.580 --> 00:43:33.180
先舔我  再舔公鸡  因为你害他流鼻血
Then you'll swallow Rooster's.  You broke his nose.

00:43:33.390 --> 00:43:35.510
他应该得到偿还
He ought to have something to show for it.

00:43:35.720 --> 00:43:37.590
它进我的嘴  就跟你分家
You put it in my mouth, you lose it.

00:43:37.790 --> 00:43:40.390
不  你没搞懂
No, you don't understand.

00:43:40.730 --> 00:43:43.750
我会用钻子刺穿你耳朵
Do that and I'll put all eight inches of this in your ear.

00:43:43.960 --> 00:43:47.420
