You know how to read, you ignorant fuck?

00:44:09.960 --> 00:44:11.050
亲爱的
Honey!

00:44:12.990 --> 00:44:14.720
你不该损我
You shouldn't!

00:44:17.400 --> 00:44:20.300
伯格斯没逼他吹喇叭
Bogs didn't put anything in Andy's mouth.

00:44:20.570 --> 00:44:22.630
其他两个也不敢
And neither did his friends.

00:44:23.070 --> 00:44:26.900
他们把安迪打个半死
What they did do is beat him within an inch of his life.

00:44:27.570 --> 00:44:30.070
在医务室里待了一个月
Andy spent a month in the infirmary.

00:44:30.880 --> 00:44:33.400
伯格斯被关禁闭一周
Bogs spent a week in the hole.

00:44:37.480 --> 00:44:39.010
时间到
Time's up, Bogs.

00:44:42.820 --> 00:44:44.480
遵命  头儿
It's your world, boss.

00:44:47.760 --> 00:44:50.560
回牢房准备点名
Return to your cellblocks for evening count.

00:44:50.760 --> 00:44:53.430
全部回牢房
All prisoners report for lock down.

00:45:08.350 --> 00:45:09.370
什么事？
What?

00:45:22.030 --> 00:45:24.550
-他想去哪儿？  -抓住脚
-Where's he going?  -Grab his ankles.

00:45:26.230 --> 00:45:31.640
不要……救命！
No...help!

00:45:35.310 --> 00:45:37.900
此后  有两件事再也没发生过
Two things never happened again after that.

00:45:38.180 --> 00:45:41.310
三姐妹再也没碰安迪
The Sisters never laid a finger on Andy again.

00:45:42.150 --> 00:45:44.640
伯格斯再也无法走路
And Bogs would never walk again.

00:45:45.820 --> 00:45:49.310
他被转送到低戒护的医院
They transferred him to a minimum-security hospital upstate.

00:45:49.520 --> 00:45:52.290
我只知道他的余生
To my knowledge, he lived out the rest of his days...

00:45:52.490 --> 00:45:54.320
全靠吸管进食
drinking his food through a straw.

00:45:55.330 --> 00:45:59.430
我想热烈欢迎安迪出院
Andy could use a nice welcome back when he gets out of the infirmary.

00:46:01.170 --> 00:46:02.730
没问题
Sounds good to us.

00:46:03.000 --> 00:46:05.490
咱们欠他的酒
I figure we owe him that much for the beer.

00:46:06.240 --> 00:46:08.500
他喜欢下棋
The man likes to play chess.

00:46:09.010 --> 00:46:10.910
