Let's get him some rocks.

00:46:43.540 --> 00:46:44.770
各位！
Guys!

00:46:45.550 --> 00:46:46.600
我找到一块
I got one.

00:46:46.810 --> 00:46:48.300
快瞧！
I got one. Look!

00:46:50.220 --> 00:46:54.280
那不是皂石 也不是雪花石
Heywood, that isn't soapstone! And it ain't alabaster either.

00:46:54.490 --> 00:46:56.390
你他妈是地质学家？
What are you, a fucking geologist?

00:46:56.590 --> 00:46:58.320
他说的没错
He's right. It ain't.

00:46:58.530 --> 00:47:01.430
-那这是什么？  -马粪蛋
-What the hell is it then? -It's a horse apple.

00:47:02.400 --> 00:47:04.800
-胡说!  -没有  就是马粪
-Bullshit!  -No, horseshit.

00:47:05.000 --> 00:47:06.490
