Petrified.

00:47:11.970 --> 00:47:13.960
天哪
God!

00:47:15.480 --> 00:47:16.670
他妈的
Damn!

00:47:16.980 --> 00:47:21.210
错误难免  但众志成城
Despite a few hitches, the boys came through in fine style.

00:47:21.420 --> 00:47:23.410
在安迪出院前一周
And by the weekend he was due back...

00:47:23.620 --> 00:47:27.310
石头多得够他刻一辈子
we had enough rocks saved up to keep him busy till rapture.

00:47:28.160 --> 00:47:30.650
同时到了一大批货
Also got a big shipment in that week.

00:47:30.920 --> 00:47:32.050
烟
Cigarettes...

00:47:32.260 --> 00:47:33.280
口香糖
chewing gum...

00:47:33.490 --> 00:47:34.980
威士忌
sipping whisky...

00:47:35.160 --> 00:47:38.560
裸女扑克牌
playing cards with naked ladies on them. You name it.

00:47:38.900 --> 00:47:41.490
