Lock them up!

00:51:02.470 --> 00:51:04.030
差点忘了
I almost forgot.

00:51:04.470 --> 00:51:06.630
我怎能拿你的圣经
I'd hate to deprive you of this.

00:51:07.370 --> 00:51:09.310
“救赎之道，就在其中。”
Salvation lies within.

00:51:09.510 --> 00:51:10.570
