I've been reassigned to you.

00:52:14.610 --> 00:52:16.940
我听说了
I know, they told me.

00:52:17.780 --> 00:52:19.840
真想不到
Ain't that a kick in the head?

00:52:20.050 --> 00:52:22.340
来个小小巡礼吧
Well, I'll give you the dime tour.

00:52:22.550 --> 00:52:23.710
来吧
Come on.

00:52:25.120 --> 00:52:26.850
都在你眼前了
Well, here she is.

