肖申克监狱图书馆
The Shawshank Prison Library.

00:52:29.720 --> 00:52:31.710
国家地理杂志
National Geographics...

00:52:32.630 --> 00:52:35.420
读者文摘
Reader's Digest condensed books...

00:52:35.630 --> 00:52:37.220
畅销西部小说
and Louis L'Amour.

00:52:37.800 --> 00:52:39.630
