Floyd, come on.

01:34:55.700 --> 01:34:57.060
瑞德
Red.

01:34:58.340 --> 01:35:00.740
把它丢掉  好吗？
Will you throw that away, please?

01:35:06.340 --> 01:35:08.070
狗屎  不赖
Well, shit.

01:35:20.760 --> 01:35:23.560
他通过了  平均丙上
The kid passed. C + average.

01:35:23.760 --> 01:35:25.850
跟你报个喜
Thought you'd like to know.

01:35:42.080 --> 01:35:43.570
典狱长找你谈话
Warden wants to talk.

01:35:57.290 --> 01:35:58.350
在这儿？
Out here?

01:35:58.560 --> 01:36:00.790
他就是这样说的
That's what the man said.

01:36:16.910 --> 01:36:17.900
典狱长？
Warden?

01:36:18.850 --> 01:36:19.780
汤米？

01:36:26.290 --> 01:36:31.990
汤米  这次会面要你保密
I'm asking you to keep this conversation just between us.

01:36:33.500 --> 01:36:35.760
我良心深感不安
I feel awkward enough as it is.

01:36:54.220 --> 01:36:56.280
他的判决出了问题
We got a situation here.

01:36:57.150 --> 01:36:59.250
我想你明白
I think you can appreciate that.

01:36:59.460 --> 01:37:00.680
是的
Yes, sir.

01:37:00.960 --> 01:37:02.360
我明白
I sure can.

01:37:02.630 --> 01:37:06.650
这件事真使我震惊
I tell you, son, this thing really came along and knocked my wind out.

01:37:08.130 --> 01:37:10.690
我连觉都睡不好
It's got me up nights.That's the truth.

01:37:12.970 --> 01:37:14.800
我该怎么做才好
The right thing to do...

01:37:16.470 --> 01:37:20.200
有时连我也搞不清楚
sometimes it's hard to know what that is.

01:37:21.210 --> 01:37:22.640
你了解吗？
Do you understand?

01:37:24.950 --> 01:37:26.540
我需要你的协助  孩子
I need your help, son.

01:37:27.990 --> 01:37:30.150
我要有……
If I'm going to move on this...

01:37:30.490 --> 01:37:33.650
十足把握才能翻案
there can't be the least little shred of doubt.

01:37:34.390 --> 01:37:35.450
我得知道
I have to know...

01:37:35.660 --> 01:37:38.290
你所说是否实话
if what you told Dufresne was the truth.

01:37:38.500 --> 01:37:39.620
是的
Yes, sir.

01:37:39.830 --> 01:37:41.060
字字属实
Absolutely.

01:37:41.570 --> 01:37:44.560
你愿在法官及陪审团前宣誓
Would you be willing to swear before a judge and jury...

01:37:44.770 --> 01:37:46.760
并且手按圣经
with your hand on the Good Book...

01:37:46.970 --> 01:37:49.630
在上帝跟前起誓吗？
and take an oath before Almighty God himself?

01:37:49.840 --> 01:37:51.640
只要给我这个机会
Just give me that chance.

01:37:55.910 --> 01:37:57.240
我也这样想
That's what I thought.

01:38:44.330 --> 01:38:46.230
相信你已听说了
I'm sure by now you've heard.

01:38:48.000 --> 01:38:49.020
真惨
Terrible thing.

01:38:50.630 --> 01:38:52.120
年纪轻轻
A man that young...

01:38:52.440 --> 01:38:55.030
刑期剩下不到一年还要逃
less than a year to go, trying to escape.

01:38:55.570 --> 01:38:58.060
射杀他令海利伤透心
Broke Captain Hadley's heart to shoot him.

01:38:58.810 --> 01:39:00.300
千真万确
Truly, it did.

01:39:03.310 --> 01:39:05.750
我们只有忘掉这事
We just have to put it behind us.

01:39:07.420 --> 01:39:08.650
继续过日子
Move on.

01:39:10.250 --> 01:39:11.740
到此为止
I'm done.

01:39:13.060 --> 01:39:14.680
我不干了
Everything stops.

01:39:16.660 --> 01:39:18.990
你找别人帮你骗钱吧
Get someone else to run your scams.

01:39:20.260 --> 01:39:22.100
一切照旧
Nothing stops.

01:39:23.430 --> 01:39:24.590
一切
Nothing.

01:39:28.010 --> 01:39:31.100
否则我要你生不如死
Or you will do the hardest time there is.

01:39:31.510 --> 01:39:33.810
不再让警卫保护你
No more protection from the guards.

01:39:34.040 --> 01:39:38.950
不再让你一人一间牢房  把你丢到鸡奸狂当中
I'll pull you out of that 1 -bunk Hilton and cast you down with the sodomites.

01:39:40.350 --> 01:39:42.780
日日夜夜轮奸不休
You'll think you've been fucked by a train.

01:39:44.190 --> 01:39:45.680
图书馆呢？
And the library?

01:39:46.360 --> 01:39:47.350
没了
Gone.

01:39:47.960 --> 01:39:50.520
用砖头封死
Sealed off, brick by brick.

01:39:50.990 --> 01:39:53.660
在操场焚书
We'll have us a little book barbecue in the yard.

01:39:53.860 --> 01:39:55.990
几里外都看得见火光
They'll see the flames for miles.

01:39:56.200 --> 01:39:59.030
大家围着火跳红蕃舞
We'll dance around it like wild Injuns.

01:40:00.300 --> 01:40:03.300
听懂了吗？
You understand me? Catching my drift?

01:40:07.040 --> 01:40:08.910
我是笨蛋吗？
Or am I being obtuse?

01:40:20.690 --> 01:40:23.320
再关他一个月  考虑清楚
Give him another month to think about it.

01:41:10.070 --> 01:41:13.130
老婆说她很难了解我
My wife used to say I'm a hard man to know.

01:41:13.940 --> 01:41:15.780
像一本合起来的书
Like a closed book.

01:41:16.580 --> 01:41:18.610
她整天这样抱怨
Complained about it all the time.

01:41:19.550 --> 01:41:21.110
她很漂亮
She was beautiful.

01:41:23.520 --> 01:41:25.040
我那么爱她
God, I loved her.

01:41:28.760 --> 01:41:30.990
我只是不擅表达
I didn't know how to show it, that's all.

01:41:33.730 --> 01:41:35.390
是我杀了她
I killed her, Red.

01:41:37.270 --> 01:41:39.060
枪不是我开的
I didn't pull the trigger...

01:41:40.500 --> 01:41:42.230
但我害她离我远去
but I drove her away.

01:41:43.740 --> 01:41:46.440
是我的脾气秉性
That's why she died, because of me...

01:41:46.640 --> 01:41:48.010
害死了她
the way I am.

01:41:57.020 --> 01:41:58.850
但你不是杀人犯
That don't make you a murderer.

01:42:02.230 --> 01:42:03.990
只能说是差丈夫
Bad husband, maybe.

01:42:07.630 --> 01:42:10.900
可以后悔  但你无罪
Feel bad about it if you want, but you didn't pull the trigger.

01:42:11.100 --> 01:42:12.430
没错
No, I didn't.

01:42:12.840 --> 01:42:14.770
别人干的
Somebody else did.

01:42:16.010 --> 01:42:18.100
却由我受罚
And I wound up in here.

01:42:20.580 --> 01:42:22.170
大概是我命薄
Bad luck, I guess.

01:42:26.030 --> 01:42:29.030
谁都可能
It floats around.

01:42:29.850 --> 01:42:32.080
沾染霉运
It's got to land on somebody.

01:42:32.990 --> 01:42:34.890
刚好轮到我
It was my turn, that's all.

01:42:35.590 --> 01:42:38.360
我被卷入龙卷风
I was in the path of the tornado.

01:42:44.300 --> 01:42:48.260
只是没想到刮了这么久
I just didn't expect the storm would last as long as it has.

01:42:52.610 --> 01:42:54.300
你有可能假释吗？
Think you'll ever get out of here?

01:42:55.550 --> 01:42:56.570
我？
Me?

01:42:59.550 --> 01:43:00.540
有吧
Yeah.

01:43:01.890 --> 01:43:04.180
要等我老得发须花白
One day, when I got a long, white beard...

01:43:04.390 --> 01:43:08.480
神智不清才行
and two or three marbles rolling around upstairs.

01:43:09.590 --> 01:43:11.220
我跟你说我要去哪儿
I tell you where I'd go.

01:43:12.700 --> 01:43:14.360
芝华塔尼欧
Zihuatanejo.

01:43:15.230 --> 01:43:16.430
哪里？
Say what?

01:43:16.730 --> 01:43:18.560
芝华塔尼欧
Zihuatanejo.

01:43:19.500 --> 01:43:21.160
在墨西哥
It's in Mexico.

01:43:22.540 --> 01:43:24.670
太平洋边的小地方
A little place on the Pacific Ocean.

01:43:25.810 --> 01:43:29.750
-知道墨西哥人怎样说太平洋的吗？  -不知道
-You know what the Mexicans say about the Pacific? -No.

01:43:30.410 --> 01:43:32.410
那是没有回忆的海洋
They say it has no memory.

01:43:34.380 --> 01:43:37.050
我要在那度此余生
That's where I want to live the rest of my life.

01:43:38.690 --> 01:43:41.180
没有回忆的温暖地
A warm place with no memory.

01:43:44.430 --> 01:43:46.360
在海边
Open up a little hotel...

01:43:48.070 --> 01:43:49.560
开个小旅馆
right on the beach.

01:43:50.170 --> 01:43:52.360
买条破船
Buy some worthless old boat...

01:43:52.900 --> 01:43:54.530
整修一新
and fix it up new.

01:43:57.270 --> 01:43:58.500
载客出海
Take my guests out...

01:43:59.340 --> 01:44:00.710
包船海钓
charter fishing.

01:44:04.550 --> 01:44:06.280
芝华塔尼欧
Zihuatanejo.

01:44:09.820 --> 01:44:13.690
你在那地方也大有可为
In a place like that, I could use a man that knows how to get things.

01:44:20.230 --> 01:44:23.060
我在外头吃不开的
I don't think I could make it on the outside.

01:44:29.740 --> 01:44:31.800
我一生都耗在肖申克
I been in here most of my life.

01:44:33.240 --> 01:44:35.010
我已经体制化了
I'm an institutional man now.

01:44:35.910 --> 01:44:37.640
就像老布
Just like Brooks was.

01:44:39.120 --> 01:44:40.810
你别小看自己
You underestimate yourself.

01:44:41.390 --> 01:44:42.980
我不这么认为
I don't think so.

01:44:46.820 --> 01:44:50.760
我在牢里让你有求必应
In here I'm the guy who can get things for you, sure, but...

01:44:51.530 --> 01:44:54.050
一出社会  电话簿里样样有
outside all you need is the Yellow Pages.

01:44:54.260 --> 01:44:56.490
但我连查都不会查
Hell, I wouldn't know where to begin.

01:44:58.640 --> 01:45:00.260
太平洋？
Pacific Ocean?

01:45:00.670 --> 01:45:01.900
狗屁
Shit.

01:45:02.270 --> 01:45:04.470
大的我心都毛了
Scare me to death, something that big.

01:45:04.670 --> 01:45:05.970
我不会
Not me.

01:45:07.180 --> 01:45:09.940
老婆和她情夫不是我杀的
I didn't shoot my wife,and I didn't shoot her lover.

01:45:11.680 --> 01:45:14.910
我犯的错已还清
Whatever mistakes I made,I've paid for them and then some.

01:45:15.950 --> 01:45:17.440
一间旅店  一叶扁舟
That hotel, that boat...

01:45:19.220 --> 01:45:21.450
要求并不过份
I don't think that's too much to ask.

01:45:26.360 --> 01:45:28.800
你不该有此妄想
You shouldn't be doing this to yourself.

01:45:29.000 --> 01:45:31.020
完全痴人说梦
This is just shitty pipe dreams.

01:45:31.470 --> 01:45:33.960
墨西哥和这儿
Mexico is way down there and you're in here...

01:45:34.140 --> 01:45:35.700
天南地北
and that's the way it is.

01:45:36.040 --> 01:45:38.870
说的没错
Yeah, right. That's the way it is.

01:45:40.380 --> 01:45:42.780
远隔天涯海角
It's down there and I'm in here.

01:45:45.350 --> 01:45:48.080
我猜是人就得二选一
I guess it comes down to a simple choice.

01:45:50.990 --> 01:45:52.480
要么忙着活……
Get busy living...

01:45:53.860 --> 01:45:55.880
要么忙着死
or get busy dying.

01:45:59.460 --> 01:46:00.690
安迪
Andy.

01:46:04.470 --> 01:46:05.560
瑞德
Red.

01:46:08.000 --> 01:46:10.730
等你假释后  帮我个忙
If you ever get out of here,do me a favor.

01:46:10.940 --> 01:46:13.210
没问题  你说
Sure, Andy. Anything.

01:46:15.080 --> 01:46:18.950
巴克斯顿有个大草场  知道巴克斯顿吗？
There's a big hayfield up near Buxton.You know where Buxton is?

01:46:20.420 --> 01:46:23.550
-那一带草场多得很  -有一处与众不同
-A lot of hayfields up there. -One in particular.

01:46:23.750 --> 01:46:27.690
那里有长石墙  北端还有大橡树
It's got a long rock wall with a big oak tree at the north end.

01:46:27.890 --> 01:46:30.760
美得像福斯特的诗
It's like something out of a Robert Frost poem.

01:46:31.700 --> 01:46:34.190
我在那儿向她求婚
It's where I asked my wife to marry me.

01:46:35.600 --> 01:46:37.690
我们去野餐
We went there for a picnic...

01:46:38.100 --> 01:46:40.190
在橡树下做爱
and made love under that oak...

01:46:40.870 --> 01:46:43.100
我开口  她首肯
and I asked and she said yes.

01:46:47.110 --> 01:46:48.940
答应我  瑞德
Promise me, Red.

01:46:49.780 --> 01:46:51.410
如果你终获假释
If you ever get out...

01:46:51.620 --> 01:46:53.110
去找到那个地方
find that spot.

01:46:54.280 --> 01:46:59.120
石墙底下有一块奇石
At the base of that wall, there's a rock that has no earthly business in Maine.

01:47:00.260 --> 01:47:03.280
黑色火山玻璃石
Piece of black, volcanic glass.

01:47:05.960 --> 01:47:08.620
底下埋着给你的东西
Something's buried under it I want you to have.

01:47:09.400 --> 01:47:10.630
是什么？
What, Andy?

01:47:11.070 --> 01:47:12.800
你埋着什么？
What's buried under there?

01:47:14.400 --> 01:47:16.270
你搬开它
You'll have to pry it up...

01:47:16.470 --> 01:47:17.740
就知道了
to see.

01:47:23.650 --> 01:47:25.580
你们听我说
No, I'm telling you. The guy is...

01:47:26.250 --> 01:47:27.980
他胡言乱语
He's talking funny.

01:47:29.090 --> 01:47:30.780
我真担心他
I'm really worried about him.

01:47:31.190 --> 01:47:32.620
我们要盯紧他
Let's keep an eye on him.

01:47:32.820 --> 01:47:36.090
白天不要紧  晚上孤伶伶的
That's fine during the day, but at night he's all alone.

01:47:37.530 --> 01:47:38.650
天哪
Oh, Lord.

01:47:40.000 --> 01:47:41.590
怎么了？
What?

01:47:42.330 --> 01:47:45.100
安迪今天到载货区
Andy come down to the loading dock today.

01:47:45.300 --> 01:47:47.400
问我要一条绳子
He asked me for a length of rope.

01:47:47.600 --> 01:47:50.300
-绳子？  -六尺长
Rope? Six feet long.

01:47:50.540 --> 01:47:51.910
你给了他？
And you gave it to him.

01:47:52.780 --> 01:47:54.570
为什么不给？
Sure. Why wouldn't I?

01:47:54.780 --> 01:47:58.710
-天啊  赫伍  -我怎么想得到？
-Jesus! Heywood. -How was I supposed to know?

01:47:59.120 --> 01:48:00.670
你忘了老布？
Remember Brooks Hatlen?

01:48:00.850 --> 01:48:04.620
不  安迪不会寻短
Andy would never do that.

01:48:05.220 --> 01:48:06.280
绝对不会
Never.

01:48:08.360 --> 01:48:09.690
谁知道呢？
I don't know.

01:48:12.530 --> 01:48:14.550
人的忍耐是有限度的
Every man has his breaking point.

01:48:16.900 --> 01:48:19.160
动作快  我要回家
Lickety-split.Want to get home.

01:48:19.470 --> 01:48:21.230
马上好了
Just about finished, sir.

01:48:38.360 --> 01:48:39.980
今晚要存三笔
Three deposits tonight.

01:48:47.960 --> 01:48:49.860
把衣物送洗
Get my stuff down to the laundry.

01:48:50.070 --> 01:48:51.690
把鞋擦亮
And shine my shoes.

01:48:51.900 --> 01:48:54.840
-要擦得雪亮  -是  先生
-I want them looking like mirrors. -Yes, sir.

01:49:00.340 --> 01:49:01.830
你回来真好  安迪
It's good having you back.

01:49:02.750 --> 01:49:04.610
没有你可差多了
Place wasn't the same without you.

01:49:51.490 --> 01:49:52.550
熄灯
Lights out!

01:50:25.400 --> 01:50:27.920
我也曾熬过孤寂长夜
I've had some long nights in stir.

01:50:28.470 --> 01:50:31.130
独自在心中思东想西
Alone in the dark with nothing but your thoughts...

01:50:31.330 --> 01:50:34.000
时间慢得如同刀割
time can draw out like a blade.

01:50:39.340 --> 01:50:42.330
那是我毕生最长的一夜
That was the longest night of my life.

01:50:58.190 --> 01:50:59.350
清点人数！
Give me a count!

01:51:03.870 --> 01:51:07.670
-南三层到齐  -北四层到齐
Tier 3 south, clear!

01:51:08.140 --> 01:51:09.630
北三层到齐

01:51:09.840 --> 01:51:13.000
二层245没人
Man missing on tier 2, cell 245!

01:51:13.210 --> 01:51:14.270
杜弗伦
Dufresne!

01:51:14.810 --> 01:51:17.250
快出来 别耍花样
Come out. You're holding up the show!

01:51:20.380 --> 01:51:23.780
等我找上门  可就重赏你的脑袋了
Don't make me come down or I'll thump your skull for you!

01:51:31.360 --> 01:51:35.200
该死  我还得等你一个  你敢耽搁我时间
Damn it, you're putting me behind! I got a schedule to keep.

01:51:35.400 --> 01:51:38.700
你最好是病了或是死了
You'd better be sick or dead in there. I shit you not!

01:51:38.900 --> 01:51:40.230
听见没有？
You hear me?

01:51:46.340 --> 01:51:48.440
噢  我的上帝
Oh, my Holy God.

01:52:05.430 --> 01:52:07.990
这一分区每人都要问
I want every man on this cellblock questioned.

01:52:08.430 --> 01:52:10.990
-先从他朋友开始  -谁？
-Start with that friend of his. -Who?

01:52:11.170 --> 01:52:12.570
他
Him.

01:52:13.570 --> 01:52:15.130
打开237
Open 237.

01:52:18.640 --> 01:52:22.300
什么叫“他不见了”？  这算什么鬼话？
What do you mean, "He just wasn't here"? Don't say that to me.

01:52:23.180 --> 01:52:24.510
你再说一次试试
Don't tell me that again.

01:52:24.710 --> 01:52:25.740
但他真的不见了
But sir, he wasn't.

01:52:25.980 --> 01:52:29.440
我没长眼睛吗？
I can see that, Haig! Think I'm blind?

01:52:30.120 --> 01:52:31.520
你是这个意思？
Is that what you're saying?

01:52:31.720 --> 01:52:34.380
-我眼瞎了？  -不敢  长官
-Am I blind, Haig? -No, sir!

01:52:35.290 --> 01:52:37.780
你呢？ 你瞎了吗？
What about you. You blind?

01:52:38.290 --> 01:52:40.850
-你说这是什么？  -昨晚的点名记录
-Tell me what this is. -Last night's count.

01:52:41.060 --> 01:52:44.360
上面明明写着杜弗伦
You see Dufresne's name there? I sure do. Right there.

01:52:44.570 --> 01:52:45.900
“杜弗伦”
"Dufresne."

01:52:47.570 --> 01:52:49.060
熄灯时
He was in his cell...

01:52:49.270 --> 01:52:50.300
他在牢里
at lights out.

01:52:50.470 --> 01:52:53.410
早上应该也在才对
Reasonable he'd be here in the morning.

01:52:53.740 --> 01:52:55.370
把他找到
I want him found.

01:52:55.580 --> 01:52:59.040
一刻不能拖  现在就找！
Not tomorrow, not after breakfast. Now!

01:52:59.280 --> 01:53:00.480
是  长官
Yes, sir.

01:53:01.480 --> 01:53:05.280
搜人去  快点
Let's go. Move your butts.

01:53:07.160 --> 01:53:08.150
站好
Stand.

01:53:09.590 --> 01:53:10.650
你说
Well?

01:53:14.100 --> 01:53:15.090
说什么？
Well, what?

01:53:15.300 --> 01:53:18.760
你们俩成天粘在一起
I see you two all the time.You're thick as thieves, you are.

01:53:19.840 --> 01:53:21.330
他一定说过什么
He must have said something.

01:53:22.070 --> 01:53:23.600
报告典狱长
No, sir, Warden.

01:53:23.940 --> 01:53:24.930
没有
Not a word.

01:53:26.780 --> 01:53:29.340
那真是奇迹了
Lord, it's a miracle!

01:53:29.950 --> 01:53:32.510
人像屁一样凭空消失
Man vanished like a fart in the wind.

01:53:33.180 --> 01:53:34.340
不见踪影
Nothing left...

01:53:35.180 --> 01:53:37.910
只剩一堆石头
but some damn rocks on a windowsill.

01:53:38.120 --> 01:53:40.850
还有墙上那骚货  问问她吧
And that cupcake on the wall. Let's ask her.

01:53:41.060 --> 01:53:42.820
也许她知道些什么
Maybe she knows.

01:53:43.060 --> 01:53:45.790
你来说  短裤妞儿
What say there, fuzzy-britches? Feel like talking?

01:53:47.230 --> 01:53:48.530
她不会说的
Guess not.

01:53:49.100 --> 01:53:51.290
别人不说  为何她要说
Why should she be any different?

01:53:52.370 --> 01:53:54.030
没错  你们有预谋
This is a conspiracy.

01:53:54.670 --> 01:53:56.500
就是这样
That's what this is.

01:53:57.110 --> 01:54:00.840
一个超级大阴谋
One big, damn conspiracy!

01:54:01.110 --> 01:54:03.100
每个人都有份
And everyone's in on it!

01:54:03.750 --> 01:54:04.910
包括她
Including her!

01:54:39.950 --> 01:54:41.640
1966年
In 1966...

01:54:41.850 --> 01:54:44.250
安迪·杜弗伦逃离……
Andy Dufresne escaped...

01:54:44.450 --> 01:54:46.010
肖申克监狱
from Shawshank Prison.

01:54:48.260 --> 01:54:50.820
狱方只寻获泥渍囚衣
All they found was a muddy set of prison clothes...

01:54:51.460 --> 01:54:52.990
一块肥皂
a bar of soap...

01:54:53.200 --> 01:54:54.750
和一把石锤
and an old rock hammer...

01:54:54.960 --> 01:54:57.460
一把几乎解体的石锤
damn near worn down to the nub.

01:55:01.940 --> 01:55:06.710
我曾夸口要花六百年才能挖通的隧道
I had thought it'd take a man 600 years to tunnel through the wall with it.

01:55:07.340 --> 01:55:09.970
安迪花了不到20年
Old Andy did it in less than 20.

01:55:28.260 --> 01:55:30.560
他喜爱研究地质
Oh, Andy loved geology.

01:55:31.330 --> 01:55:34.500
碎石令他想一探究竟
I imagine it appealed to his meticulous nature.

01:55:34.900 --> 01:55:36.740
刑期如同
An ice age here...

01:55:37.170 --> 01:55:39.660
冰河时代
million years of mountain building there.

01:55:40.680 --> 01:55:43.510
地质学探讨压力及时间
Geology is the study of pressure and time.

01:55:44.350 --> 01:55:46.340
这就是凿通的关键——
That's all it takes, really.

01:55:47.080 --> 01:55:48.180
压力
Pressure...

01:55:48.820 --> 01:55:50.080
时间
and time.

01:55:51.420 --> 01:55:53.480
和一张够大的海报
That and a big goddamn poster.

01:55:57.290 --> 01:55:58.450
就像我说的
Like I said...

01:55:58.960 --> 01:56:02.950
在牢里  没事也得找事做
in prison, a man will do anything to keep his mind occupied.

01:56:05.770 --> 01:56:10.570
原来安迪的嗜好  就是把他的牢墙
Seems Andy's favorite hobby was toting his wall out into the exercise yard...

01:56:11.110 --> 01:56:13.040
一次一把地搬到操场上
a handful at a time.

01:56:14.340 --> 01:56:16.400
大概就在汤米死后
I guess after Tommy was killed...

01:56:16.610 --> 01:56:19.580
安迪决定不再久留
Andy decided he'd been here long enough.

01:56:19.780 --> 01:56:22.340
动作快  我要回家
Lickety-split.I want to get home.

01:56:23.090 --> 01:56:25.110
马上就好
I'm just about finished, sir.

01:56:46.580 --> 01:56:48.510
今晚要存三笔
Three deposits tonight.

01:56:55.820 --> 01:56:58.120
安迪奉命行事
Andy did like he was told.

01:56:58.320 --> 01:57:01.810
把鞋子擦得雪亮
Buffed those shoes to a high mirror-shine.

01:57:05.500 --> 01:57:07.790
警卫都没注意
The guards simply didn't notice.

01:57:08.100 --> 01:57:09.590
我也没有
Neither did I.

01:57:09.770 --> 01:57:11.290
说真的
I mean, seriously...

01:57:11.500 --> 01:57:14.490
谁会注意别人的鞋子
how often do you really look at a man's shoes?

01:59:18.060 --> 01:59:21.220
安迪就这样爬向自由
Andy crawled to freedom through 500 yards...

01:59:21.460 --> 01:59:24.800
在恶臭中匍匐五百码
of shit-smelling foulness I can't even imagine.

01:59:25.800 --> 01:59:28.130
换我才不干呢
Or maybe I just don't want to.

01:59:32.540 --> 01:59:34.910
五百码
Five hundred yards.

01:59:35.410 --> 01:59:38.470
有五个足球场那么长
That's the length of five football fields.

01:59:39.120 --> 01:59:41.680
接近半英里
Just shy of half a mile.

02:00:36.910 --> 02:00:41.500
次日清晨  在拉寇儿坦露她的秘密之时
The next morning, right about the time Raquel was spilling her secret...

02:00:41.810 --> 02:00:44.640
一个从未现世的人
a man nobody ever laid eyes on before...

02:00:44.880 --> 02:00:47.470
走进缅因国家银行
strolled into the Maine National Bank.

02:00:48.050 --> 02:00:51.210
在那之前  他不是实体
Until that moment, he didn't exist.

02:00:51.790 --> 02:00:54.150
-只存在于文件上  -有何贵干？
-Except on paper. -May I help you?

02:00:54.560 --> 02:00:56.490
他各种证件都有
He had all the proper ID...

02:00:56.690 --> 02:01:00.390
驾照  出生证  社会保险卡
driver's license, birth certificate, Social Security card...

02:01:00.830 --> 02:01:03.360
签名分毫不差
And the signature was a spot-on match.

02:01:03.570 --> 02:01:06.660
失去您的生意令我真心遗憾
I must say I'm sorry to be losing your business.

02:01:06.870 --> 02:01:08.600
祝您侨居愉快
I hope you'll enjoy living abroad.

02:01:09.410 --> 02:01:10.500
谢谢
Thank you.

02:01:11.170 --> 02:01:12.330
一定的
I'm sure I will.

02:01:13.240 --> 02:01:16.580
这是银行本票  就这样吗？
Here's your cashier's check, sir. Will there be anything else?

02:01:16.780 --> 02:01:17.770
麻烦你
Please.

02:01:18.350 --> 02:01:20.840
帮我寄出去好吗？
Would you add this to your outgoing mail?

02:01:21.350 --> 02:01:22.540
乐意之至
I'd be happy to.

02:01:24.350 --> 02:01:25.680
-再会  -走好
-Good day, sir. -Good day.

02:01:26.620 --> 02:01:31.060
那天上午史帝文先后去了十多家银行
Mr. Stevens visited nearly a dozen banks in the Portland area that morning.

02:01:31.530 --> 02:01:33.120
总共加起来
All told, he blew town...

02:01:33.330 --> 02:01:38.160
提走了诺顿37万美金
with better than $370,000 of Warden Norton's money.

02:01:38.870 --> 02:01:41.630
作为十九年冤狱的补偿
Severance pay for 19 years.

02:01:48.880 --> 02:01:51.070
早上好 这里是《波特兰号角日报》
Good morning, Portland Daily Bugle.

02:02:43.930 --> 02:02:46.870
你是海利吗？  你有权保持沉默
Byron Hadley? You have the right to remain silent.

02:02:47.140 --> 02:02:51.570
从现在起 你所说的一切 都将可能成为呈堂证供
If you give up this right, anything you say can be held against you in court.

02:02:52.010 --> 02:02:56.470
当时我没有在场  后来听说
I wasn't there to see, but I hear Byron Hadley sobbed like a girl...

02:02:56.680 --> 02:02:58.170
海利被人带走的时候  哭得像个娘们儿
when they took him away.

02:03:04.050 --> 02:03:07.450
诺顿却无意乖乖就范
Norton had no intention of going that quietly.

02:03:23.410 --> 02:03:24.770
诺顿
Samuel Norton.

02:03:24.940 --> 02:03:27.370
诺顿  我们有拘捕令  开门
We have a warrant for your arrest. Open up.

02:03:30.810 --> 02:03:33.210
把门打开
Open the door.

02:03:33.750 --> 02:03:35.010
我不清楚是哪一把
I'm not sure which key.

02:03:44.690 --> 02:03:47.360
别自找麻烦  诺顿
Make it easy on yourself, Norton!

02:03:58.610 --> 02:04:02.070
我猜他脑中最后一件事
I like to think the last thing that went through his head...

02:04:02.280 --> 02:04:03.870
除了枪子儿
other than that bullet...

02:04:04.080 --> 02:04:08.520
就是在想安迪为何能整倒他
was to wonder how the hell Andy Dufresne ever got the best of him.

02:04:11.020 --> 02:04:14.480
典狱长呜呼后不久
Not long after the warden deprived us of his company...

02:04:14.760 --> 02:04:16.820
我收到一张明信片
I got a postcard in the mail.

02:04:18.290 --> 02:04:21.130
没写字  但有邮戳
It was blank, but the postmark said...

02:04:21.330 --> 02:04:23.460
来自德州汉考克堡
Fort Hancock, Texas.

02:04:24.000 --> 02:04:25.360
汉考克堡
Fort Hancock...

02:04:25.630 --> 02:04:27.360
就在边境线上
right on the border.

02:04:27.770 --> 02:04:29.760
安迪就是从那里出境的
That's where Andy crossed.

02:04:30.340 --> 02:04:34.470
驾着敞蓬车驶向南方
When I picture him heading south in his own car with the top down...

02:04:34.810 --> 02:04:37.040
想到这画面就令我开怀大笑
it always makes me laugh.

02:04:38.880 --> 02:04:40.440
安迪·杜弗伦
Andy Dufresne...

02:04:40.820 --> 02:04:42.840
爬过肮脏的下水道
who crawled through a river of shit...

02:04:43.050 --> 02:04:45.450
出来已焕然一新
and came out clean on the other side.

02:04:46.290 --> 02:04:47.650
安迪·杜弗伦
Andy Dufresne...

02:04:48.460 --> 02:04:50.050
向太平洋驶去
headed for the Pacific.

02:04:53.030 --> 02:04:55.190
海利掐住他喉咙说
Hadley's got him by the throat, right?

02:04:55.400 --> 02:04:59.200
“他活的不耐烦了。”
He says, "I believe this boy's about to have himself an accident."

02:04:59.400 --> 02:05:02.270
老友们常聊起他
Those of us who knew him best talk about him often.

02:05:02.940 --> 02:05:04.630
他那些惊人之举
I swear, the stuff he pulled...

02:05:04.840 --> 02:05:07.810
“请我朋友喝啤酒吧……”
"My friends could use a couple of beers."

02:05:08.140 --> 02:05:09.800
他真的做到了！
And he got it!

02:05:11.050 --> 02:05:13.450
有时我会感伤
Sometimes it makes me sad, though...

02:05:13.720 --> 02:05:15.150
他的离去
Andy being gone.

02:05:15.850 --> 02:05:17.050
我不得不提醒自己
I have to remind myself that...

02:05:17.050 --> 02:05:18.980
有些鸟儿是注定不会被关在牢笼里的
some birds aren't meant to be caged.

02:05:20.460 --> 02:05:22.520
它们的每一片羽毛都闪耀着自由的光辉
Their feathers are just too bright.

02:05:24.230 --> 02:05:25.960
当它们盘旋飞离之时
And when they fly away...

02:05:26.400 --> 02:05:30.800
你会由衷地祝贺它们获得自由
the part of you that knows it was a sin to lock them up does rejoice.

02:05:31.870 --> 02:05:33.130
无奈的是
But still...

02:05:33.600 --> 02:05:37.940
你得继续在这乏味之地苟活
the place you live in is that much more drab and empty that they're gone.

02:05:42.140 --> 02:05:44.510
我真怀念这位友伴
I guess I just miss my friend.

02:06:08.970 --> 02:06:10.130
请坐
Please sit down.

02:06:15.980 --> 02:06:17.540
埃利斯·博伊德·瑞丁
Ellis Boyd Redding...

02:06:18.080 --> 02:06:21.350
根据你的材料 你的终身监禁已经服满40年
your files say you've served 40 years of a life sentence.

02:06:22.150 --> 02:06:24.280
你改过自新了吗？
You feel you've been rehabilitated?

02:06:26.160 --> 02:06:27.710
改过自新？
Rehabilitated?

02:06:29.760 --> 02:06:31.660
噢  让我想想
Well, now, let me see.

02:06:32.660 --> 02:06:34.990
我不大明白这个词的含义
I don't have any idea what that means.

02:06:37.100 --> 02:06:39.360
就是说准备好重返社会
It means you're ready to rejoin society...

02:06:39.940 --> 02:06:42.270
我当然明白你的意思  年轻人
I know what you think it means, sonny.

02:06:44.440 --> 02:06:46.430
对我而言  这只是个术语
To me it's just a made-up word.

02:06:47.780 --> 02:06:50.110
政客发明的术语
A politician's word so that...

02:06:50.550 --> 02:06:54.070
好让你们穿西装打领带
young fellas like yourself can wear a suit and a tie...

02:06:54.550 --> 02:06:56.140
有活干
and have a job.

02:06:58.120 --> 02:07:00.210
你到底想了解什么？
What do you really want to know?

02:07:00.990 --> 02:07:02.960
我后悔犯罪吗？
Am I sorry for what I did?

02:07:03.390 --> 02:07:04.550
你后悔吗？
Well, are you?

02:07:06.460 --> 02:07:09.300
我没有一天不后悔
There's not a day goes by I don't feel regret.

02:07:10.670 --> 02:07:14.120
但并非因为关在这里 也不为讨好你们
Not because I'm in here or because you think I should.

02:07:17.610 --> 02:07:20.170
回首前尘往事
I look back on the way I was then...

02:07:22.310 --> 02:07:23.470
那个
a young...

02:07:24.580 --> 02:07:28.070
犯下重罪的小笨蛋
stupid kid who committed that terrible crime.

02:07:31.090 --> 02:07:32.780
我想跟他沟通
I want to talk to him.

02:07:34.720 --> 02:07:37.210
我试图讲道理
I want to try and talk some sense to him.

02:07:37.930 --> 02:07:39.860
让他明了
Tell him the way things are.

02:07:41.960 --> 02:07:43.400
但我办不到
But I can't.

02:07:45.600 --> 02:07:47.590
那个少年早就不见了
That kid's long gone...

02:07:48.800 --> 02:07:51.570
只剩下我垂老之躯
and this old man is all that's left.

02:07:52.980 --> 02:07:54.470
我得接受事实
I got to live with that.

02:07:55.810 --> 02:07:57.510
改过自新？
Rehabilitated?

02:07:57.880 --> 02:07:59.710
狗屁不通的词儿
It's just a bullshit word.

02:08:00.650 --> 02:08:05.420
盖章吧  别浪费我的时间
So you go on and stamp your forms,sonny, and stop wasting my time.

02:08:06.660 --> 02:08:08.920
告诉你一句实话
Because to tell you the truth...

02:08:09.260 --> 02:08:11.250
我他妈的不在乎
I don't give a shit.

02:09:37.780 --> 02:09:39.180
你的 小姐
Here you go, miss.

02:09:42.120 --> 02:09:43.140
可以上厕所吗？
Restroom break?

02:09:48.960 --> 02:09:53.490
别一尿尿就来报告  要去就去  懂吗?
You don't need to ask me every time you need to go take a piss. Just go.

02:09:54.530 --> 02:09:56.120
是
Yes.

02:10:06.540 --> 02:10:09.600
我报告了40年
Forty years I've been asking permission to piss.

02:10:10.450 --> 02:10:13.440
不报告  一滴也挤不出
I can't squeeze a drop without say-so.

02:10:16.950 --> 02:10:19.110
我得面对一个残酷的事实
There's a harsh truth to face.

02:10:20.790 --> 02:10:23.690
在狱外我根本混不下去
No way I'm going to make it on the outside.

02:10:31.570 --> 02:10:35.260
我一心想违犯假释
All I do anymore is think of ways to break my parole...

02:10:36.070 --> 02:10:38.560
也许就能重返肖申克
so maybe they'd send me back.

02:10:43.750 --> 02:10:46.180
活在恐惧中真是糟糕
Terrible thing, to live in fear.

02:10:47.080 --> 02:10:48.740
老布体会过
Brooks Hatlen knew it.

02:10:48.950 --> 02:10:50.890
他看透了
Knew it all too well.

02:10:52.490 --> 02:10:55.890
我只想回到有意义的地方
All I want is to be back where things make sense.

02:10:56.330 --> 02:10:59.060
不必整天担惊受怕
Where I won't have to be afraid all the time.

02:11:01.060 --> 02:11:03.430
只有一件事阻止了我
Only one thing stops me.

02:11:04.870 --> 02:11:07.270
我向安迪做过承诺
A promise I made to Andy.

02:11:27.790 --> 02:11:28.920
到了
There it is.

02:11:39.530 --> 02:11:41.200
非常感谢您
Much obliged, sir.

02:15:20.520 --> 02:15:21.780
“亲爱的瑞德：”
Dear Red:

02:15:22.020 --> 02:15:24.510
“见到这封信的时候，你已经出狱了。”
If you're reading this,you've gotten out...

02:15:24.690 --> 02:15:28.750
“既然走了这么远的路，干脆再走远一点吧。”
and if you've come this far,maybe you'd come a bit further.

02:15:29.030 --> 02:15:31.520
“你还记得那个地方的名字，是吗？”
You remember the name of the town, don't you?

02:15:33.800 --> 02:15:35.290
“芝华塔尼欧。”
Zihuatanejo.

02:15:36.940 --> 02:15:40.530
“请来帮我实现计划，”
I could use a good man to help me get my project on wheels.

02:15:41.040 --> 02:15:44.570
“我备妥棋盘等着你。”
I'll keep an eye out for you, and the chessboard ready.

02:15:45.380 --> 02:15:46.780
“记住，瑞德，”
Remember, Red...

02:15:47.120 --> 02:15:49.210
“心怀希望是一件好事，”
hope is a good thing...

02:15:49.420 --> 02:15:51.410
“也许是最好的事。”
maybe the best of things.

02:15:51.620 --> 02:15:53.780
“心怀希望，就永远都有希望。”
And no good thing ever dies.

02:15:54.320 --> 02:15:57.190
“希望这封信，能让我再次见到你，”
I will be hoping that this letter finds you...

02:15:57.390 --> 02:15:59.120
“一个健在的你。”
and finds you well.

02:15:59.630 --> 02:16:00.860
“你的朋友”
Your friend...

02:16:01.060 --> 02:16:02.220
“安迪”
Andy.

02:16:36.060 --> 02:16:37.790
“要么忙着活，”
"Get busy living...

02:16:38.000 --> 02:16:39.900
“要么忙着死。”
or get busy dying."

02:16:42.600 --> 02:16:44.770
这话真他妈的精辟
That's goddamn right.

02:16:50.010 --> 02:16:52.140
这是生平第二次
For the second time in my life...

02:16:52.380 --> 02:16:54.940
我又犯了罪
I'm guilty of committing a crime.

02:16:56.020 --> 02:16:57.950
违反假释出城
Parole violation.

02:16:58.620 --> 02:17:02.280
我怀疑警方会设路障抓我
Of course I doubt they'll toss up any roadblocks for that.

02:17:02.960 --> 02:17:04.980
不过我这种老贼大可免了
Not for an old crook like me.

02:17:05.190 --> 02:17:07.220
去德州汉考克堡  谢谢
Fort Hancock, Texas, please.

02:17:10.900 --> 02:17:15.630
我激动得不能安坐或思考
I find I'm so excited I can barely sit still or hold a thought in my head.

02:17:16.070 --> 02:17:19.400
我想  只有真正的自由人
I think it's the excitement only a free man can feel.

02:17:19.610 --> 02:17:22.100
在踏上远征那一刻  才会生出这种
A free man at the start of a long journey...

02:17:22.310 --> 02:17:24.900
即将揭开未来神秘面纱的激动心情吧
whose conclusion is uncertain.

02:17:27.920 --> 02:17:30.580
我希望能顺利跨越边境
I hope I can make it across the border.

02:17:32.090 --> 02:17:35.110
我希望能跟重逢老友握握手
I hope to see my friend and shake his hand.

02:17:36.990 --> 02:17:41.050
我希望太平洋如梦中一般蓝
I hope the Pacific is as blue as it has been in my dreams.

02:17:42.900 --> 02:17:44.090
我希望……
I hope.